{{vgname|直到黎明|en=Until Dawn}}是由{{link-en|Supermassive Games|Supermassive Games}}開發並由[[索尼電腦娛樂|索尼電腦娛樂]]發行在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]平台的[[驚悚遊戲|驚悚]][[冒險遊戲|冒險遊戲]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/07/25/until-dawn-the-unfinished-swan-and-journey-confirmed-for-ps4?abthid=53d2a798f289c31e58000018|title=Until Dawn, The Unfinished Swan, and Journey Confirmed for PS4|publisher=IGN.com|accessdate=2014-07-25|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322155949/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/07/25/until-dawn-the-unfinished-swan-and-journey-confirmed-for-ps4?abthid=53d2a798f289c31e58000018|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在2015年8月尾開始於世界各地發售<ref name="release">{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/05/26/until-dawn-launches-on-ps4-august-25th/|title=Until Dawn Launches on PS4 August 25th|first=Pete|last=Samuels|work=PlayStation Blog|date=2015-05-26|accessdate=2015-05-26|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520112859/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/05/26/until-dawn-launches-on-ps4-august-25th/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《直到黎明》最初把平台定在[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]並支持[[PlayStation_Move|PlayStation Move]]，但後來改為以PlayStation 4為獨佔平台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/08/12/gamescom-2014-dawn-now-ps4-exclusive/ |title=Gamescom 2014: Until Dawn is Now a PS4 Exclusive, Uses the Killzone: Shadow Fall Engine (Updated) |publisher=playstationlifestyle.net |accessdate=2014-08-15 |archive-date=2016-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412025416/http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/08/12/gamescom-2014-dawn-now-ps4-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《直到黎明》在發售初期便因其視覺效果、選項、音樂和富含恐怖元素的遊戲設計獲得廣泛好評。而批評則主要集中在後半部分的劇情、鏡頭角度和人物動作。

== 遊戲玩法 ==
[[File:Until_Dawn_screenshot.jpg|thumb]]
《直到黎明》的设计使得玩家在进行多次游玩之后，可以打开多个结局，开启更多的新要素<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/07/17/until-dawn-will-redefine-the-interactive-genre/158744/|title=Until Dawn Will Redefine the Interactive Genre|first=Jason|last=O'Connell|work=Hardcore Gamer|date=2015-07-17|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423055247/https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/07/17/until-dawn-will-redefine-the-interactive-genre/158744/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每個結局持續大約遊戲時間9個小時<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/until_dawn/news/until_dawn_around_9_hours_long_has_hundreds_of_endings.html|title=Until Dawn 'around 9 hours long', 'has hundreds of endings'|first=David|last=Scammell|date=2015-08-14|accessdate=2015-08-27|work=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074312/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/until_dawn/news/until_dawn_around_9_hours_long_has_hundreds_of_endings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且遊戲採用了新的名叫「[[蝴蝶效應|蝴蝶效應]]」的遊戲系統，玩家可以任意選擇由系統給出的選項，但同時可能會令後來產生一個不可預見的後果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/until-dawn-has-hundreds-of-endings-and-thousands-of-branches-279599.phtml|title=Until Dawn has hundreds of endings and thousands of branches|first=Dale|last=North|work=Destructoid|date=2015-08-14|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2016-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126194724/https://www.destructoid.com/until-dawn-has-hundreds-of-endings-and-thousands-of-branches-279599.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。打個比方，玩家如果在前一章節拾起了一個武器的話，可能會導致在追逐場面中回到拾起武器的那個房間。在整個遊戲中，玩家會面對多次倫理和道德的困境，例如必須犧牲一個角色才可拯救他人的艱難決擇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2015/08/26/ten-tips-for-surviving-the-night-in-until-dawn/|title=10 tips for surviving the night in Until Dawn|first=Dean|last=Takakashi|work=VentureBeat|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308044211/https://venturebeat.com/2015/08/26/ten-tips-for-surviving-the-night-in-until-dawn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蝴蝶效應系統模糊了對與錯的決定之間的分界線，玩家可以使所有8個角色活著或他們8個人全部死亡，且允許出現許多不同的遊戲路線或應用場景，以及提供多種不同的結局<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/walkthroughs/14488-Until-Dawn-Best-Worst-Endings-Guide|title=Save (Or Kill) Everyone in Until Dawn With These Choices|work=The Escapist|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2017-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314210706/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/walkthroughs/14488-Until-Dawn-Best-Worst-Endings-Guide|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，另外也會因此影響存活角色結尾與警方的對話內容<ref>{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/The_Interview|title=Until Dawn "The Interview"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-08|accessdate=2015-09-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914021219/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/The_Interview|archivedate=2015年9月14日}}</ref><ref>Chris：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Chris|title=Until Dawn "Chris"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-09|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004173537/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Chris|dead-url=no}}；Emily：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Emily|title=Until Dawn "Emily"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-08|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004184227/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Emily|dead-url=no}}；Jessica：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Jessica|title=Until Dawn "Jessica"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-08|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005041737/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Jessica|dead-url=no}}；Matt：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Matt|title=Until Dawn "Matt"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-09|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004205555/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Matt|dead-url=no}}；Michael：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Michael_Munroe|title=Until Dawn "Michael Munroe"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-09|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925121955/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Michael_Munroe|dead-url=no}}；Samantha：{{cite news|url=http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Sam|title=Until Dawn "Sam"|publisher=Until Dawn Community Wikia|date=2015-09-09|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004231257/http://until-dawn.wikia.com/wiki/Sam|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《直到黎明》有著嚴格的自動保存系統，以防止玩家因後悔自己所做的決定而重新加載之前的存檔。唯一一個改變玩家選擇的方法是重新開始遊戲或玩到結尾後開始一個新的遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2015/8/17/9157213/until-dawn-supermassive-games|title=Until Dawn: The Surprising Ambition And Curious Fear of Supermassive Games|first=Philip|last=Kollar|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date=2015-08-17|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415061657/https://www.polygon.com/features/2015/8/17/9157213/until-dawn-supermassive-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲開發人員在採訪中表示《直到黎明》有「數百個結局」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/08/15/until-dawn-around-nine-hours-long-will-have-hundreds-of-endings/|title=Until Dawn "Around Nine Hours" Long, Will Have "Hundreds of Endings"|first=Alex|last=Co|publisher=Playstation Lifestyle|date=2014-08-15|accessdate=2015-04-25|archive-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921020556/http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2014/08/15/until-dawn-around-nine-hours-long-will-have-hundreds-of-endings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，得出哪一個結局取決於遊戲結束時有哪些角色活著<ref name="Smg">{{cite web|url=http://www.supermassivegames.com/games/until-dawn/|title=Until Dawn Unveiled Official Website for PS4|publisher=Supermassive Games|date=2015-03-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308212712/http://www.supermassivegames.com/games/until-dawn/|archivedate=2015年3月8日}}</ref>。

《直到黎明》著重於玩家所做的探查、[[QTE|QTE]]、發現的線索以及作出的決定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.psu.com/review/27924/Until-Dawn-Review--Choice-and-grisly-consequence|title=Until Dawn Review: Choice and grisly consequence|first=Kyle|last=Prahl|date=2015-08-24|accessdate=2015-08-27|work=PlayStation Universe|archive-date=2016-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161117204248/http://www.psu.com/review/27924/Until-Dawn-Review--Choice-and-grisly-consequence|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此遊戲有一個會記錄所有玩家發現的線索與祕密的系統，而這些線索或祕密可使玩家解開黑木森林的謎團<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2015/08/24/until-dawn-is-telltale-with-unlimited-time-funds-and-jump-scares/|title=Until Dawn is Telltale with unlimited time, funds and jump scares|first=Brenna|last=Hillier|work=VG 247|date=2015-08-24|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2019-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418203158/https://www.vg247.com/2015/08/24/until-dawn-is-telltale-with-unlimited-time-funds-and-jump-scares/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以遊戲機制或主題而言，《直到黎明》與《[[暴雨殺機|暴雨殺機]]》和《[[超能殺機：兩個靈魂|超能殺機：兩個靈魂]]》相似<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-08-25-until-dawn-may-be-the-horror-themed-heavy-rain-youve-been-waiting-for|title=Until Dawn may be the horror-themed Heavy Rain you've been waiting for|first=Thomas|last=Morgan|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-08-25|accessdate=2015-08-27|archive-date=2016-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105054414/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-08-25-until-dawn-may-be-the-horror-themed-heavy-rain-youve-been-waiting-for|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://business.financialpost.com/fp-tech-desk/post-arcade/until-dawn-review|title=Until Dawn review: A full-fledged horror movie in a surprisingly slick interactive format|first=Daniel|last=Kaszor|date=2015-08-24|accessdate=2015-08-27|work=The Financial Post|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610112108/http://business.financialpost.com/fp-tech-desk/post-arcade/until-dawn-review|dead-url=no