《直到黎明》在[[日本|日本]]成为了第六每星期销售最高的软件，销量超过17万。这游戏和《[[龍族教義|龍族教義Online]]》一起让PlayStation 4销量稍微提高了一些<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pushsquare.com/news/2015/09/japanese_sales_charts_until_dawn_and_dragons_dogma_online_give_us_something_to_write_about|title=Japanese Sales Charts: Until Dawn and Dragon's Dogma Online Give Us Something to Write About|last=Square|first=Push|date=2015-09-02|newspaper=Push Square|accessdate=2018-03-20|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224231013/https://www.pushsquare.com/news/2015/09/japanese_sales_charts_until_dawn_and_dragons_dogma_online_give_us_something_to_write_about|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月29日，此游戏在[[英国|英国]]成为了该星期的第二销售最高软件，在英国零售销售表中获得了第二，仅落后于《[[战争机器_(游戏)|战争机器：终极版]]》<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.videogamer.com/xboxone/gears_of_war_ultimate_edition/news/uk_video_game_chart_is_a_real_chart_for_real_men.html|title=UK Video Game Chart is a real chart for real men - VideoGamer.com|newspaper=VideoGamer.com|accessdate=2018-03-20|language=en-GB|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065545/http://www.videogamer.com/xboxone/gears_of_war_ultimate_edition/news/uk_video_game_chart_is_a_real_chart_for_real_men.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根据[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]，《直到黎明》在2015年8月是英国第七销售最高的游戏<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/09/10/august-2015-npd-madden-is-king-and-until-dawn-has-a-solid-showing.aspx?|title=August 2015 NPD: Madden Is King And Until Dawn Has A Solid Showing|accessdate=2018-03-20|work=Game Informer|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308094607/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/09/10/august-2015-npd-madden-is-king-and-until-dawn-has-a-solid-showing.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开发团队——Supermassive Games表示这些销量已经大大超过了他们的预期<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/10/09/supermassive-games-until-dawn-2-being-discussed-sales-surpassed-expectations/#/slide/1|title=Supermassive Games: Until Dawn 2 Being Discussed, Sales "Surpassed Expectations"|date=2015-10-09|newspaper=PlayStation LifeStyle|accessdate=2018-03-20|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223082724/https://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/10/09/supermassive-games-until-dawn-2-being-discussed-sales-surpassed-expectations/#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

