==分拆与前传==
在接受{{le|PlayStation LifeStyle|PlayStation LifeStyle}}的采访时，执行制片人彼得·薩繆爾斯（Pete Samuels）表示Supermassive Games仍在探索延续《直到黎明》故事的可能性。<ref name="playstationlifestyle.net">{{cite web|url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/10/09/supermassive-games-until-dawn-2-being-discussed-sales-surpassed-expectations/#/slide/1|title=Supermassive Games: Until Dawn 2 Being Discussed, Sales "Surpassed Expectations"|work=PlayStation LifeStyle|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223082724/https://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/10/09/supermassive-games-until-dawn-2-being-discussed-sales-surpassed-expectations/#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>索尼在2015年[[巴黎游戏周|巴黎游戏周]]上宣布了一个非典型的分拆作品，《{{le|直到黎明：血腥突袭|Until Dawn: Rush of Blood}}》，一款第一人称射击恐怖游戏，这款游戏的开发在《直到黎明》本作的开发中期开始。2016年10月13日，该作发布，为一款[[PS_VR|PS VR]]游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/10/27/until-dawn-rush-of-blood-is-a-fast-paced-arcade-shooter-for-playstation-vr/|title=Until Dawn: Rush of Blood is a "fast-paced arcade shooter" for PlayStation VR|first=Matt|last=Martin|work=[[VG247|VG247]]|date=2015-10-27|accessdate=2015-10-28|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107005954/http://www.vg247.com/2015/10/27/until-dawn-rush-of-blood-is-a-fast-paced-arcade-shooter-for-playstation-vr/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。

2017年6月，游戏《[[絕命患者|絕命患者]]》被宣称为《直到黎明》故事的前作，其设定为在该作故事发生的60年前，背景为正傳中出現過的黑木疗养院（Blackwood Sanatorium）。<ref name="51xty">{{cite web|url=https://blog.us.playstation.com/2017/06/12/the-inpatient-announced-for-ps-vr-set-60-years-before-until-dawn/|title=The Inpatient Announced for PS VR, Set 60 Years Before Until Dawn|first=Nik|last=Bowen|date=2017-06-12|website=[[PlayStation_Blog|PlayStation Blog]]|publisher=[[Sony_Interactive_Entertainment|Sony Interactive Entertainment]]|accessdate=2018-03-16|archive-date=2019-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508143517/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2017/06/12/the-inpatient-announced-for-ps-vr-set-60-years-before-until-dawn/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>该款作品在2018年1月发售。

